ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectProtocol to the North Atlantic Treaty on the Accession of the Republic of North Macedonia
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of Canada, the PROTOCOLE TO THE NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ON THE ACCESSION OF THE REPUBLIC OF NORTH MACEDONIA in order to fulfill Canada’s longstanding support for North Macedonia’s accession to the North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO).
